PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into a "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" with the KAHKEWISTAHAW BAND OF INDIANS of Saskatchewan which is designed to resolve specific claims pertaining to the setting apart of fishing grounds on its Reserve No. 72A, this reserve having been set aside in 1889 by Order in Council P.C. 1151, and (b) to accept an INSTRUMENT OF SURRENDER within the context of this settlement.

precis:
Authority (a) to enter into a "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" with the
KAHKEWISTAHAW BAND OF INDIANS of Saskatchewan which is designed to resolve
specific claims pertaining to the setting apart of fishing grounds on its
Reserve No. 72A, this reserve having been set aside in 1889 by Order in
Council P.C. 1151, and (b) to accept an INSTRUMENT OF SURRENDER within the
context of this settlement.
